node.text:
❤️Whipping up a delicious meal with Koka’s delight chicken non-fried noodle! The whole grain noodles are so springy and the chicken flavor goes really well with an egg🥚 Try pairing your noodles with some crab stick and pork meatballs and of course some chilli padi for heat! Guarantee satisfaction 👍🏻👍🏻It’s the perfect fuss free meal to whip up whenever I crave for something instant! ⁣
